# CELPIP Platform — Production-Grade Implementation Plan

A full-stack, scalable, AI-powered CELPIP exam practice platform built for production from day one.  
Stack: **Next.js 14 · FastAPI · PostgreSQL · Redis · Celery · S3 · Stripe · Clerk**

