## Tech Stack Decisions — Production Rationale

| Layer | Choice | Rationale |
|---|---|---|
| Frontend | Next.js 14 App Router + TypeScript | SSR for SEO on marketing pages; RSC for dashboard performance |
| Styling | Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui | Consistency + speed; shadcn = unstyled accessible components |
| State | React Query (TanStack) | Caching, polling, background refetch built-in |
| API | FastAPI + Pydantic v2 | Async-first, auto OpenAPI docs, strict typing |
| ORM | SQLAlchemy 2.0 (async) | Mature, type-safe, works with Alembic migrations |
| DB | PostgreSQL (managed) | ACID compliance, JSONB for rubric data, full-text search later |
| Queue | Redis + Celery | Battle-tested, supports priorities, retries, ETA |
| Auth | Clerk | Fastest to ship social + email auth; JWT tokens FastAPI can verify |
| Payments | Stripe | Industry standard; webhook-driven plan sync |
| STT | OpenAI Whisper API | Best-in-class accuracy, fast, no infra to manage for MVP |
| LLM Scoring | Multi-model abstraction (GPT-4o-mini default, hot-swappable) | Provider protocol pattern — switch model via config with zero code change |
| Storage | AWS S3 / Cloudflare R2 | Cheap, durable, pre-signed URL pattern |
| AI Calibration | Calibration store (DB table + admin UI) | Band-level sample responses injectable into system prompt, extensible per task |
| Deploy (FE) | Vercel | Zero-config Next.js, preview deployments per PR |
| Deploy (API) | Render / Railway / Fly.io | Simple Docker-based deploys, managed scaling |
| Observability | Prometheus + Grafana / Datadog | Production visibility into AI pipeline latency and cost |

